<h1>步</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">bù</span><span class=alesi>(bu4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 步 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 步</h2><div class=abo>
