-2" title="List of HSK 2 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 2 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 349</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 0710</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/代步" title="dai4 bu4">代步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/信步" title="xin4 bu4">信步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/停步" title="ting2 bu4">停步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/优步" title="You1 bu4">优步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/八步" title="Ba1 bu4">八步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/初步" title="chu1 bu4">初步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/却步" title="que4 bu4">却步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/同步" title="tong2 bu4">同步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/地步" title="di4 bu4">地步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/城步" title="Cheng2 bu4">城步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/大步" title="da4 bu4">大步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/徐步" title="xu2 bu4">徐步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/徒步" title="tu2 bu4">徒步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/快步" title="kuai4 bu4">快步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/慢步" title="man4 bu4">慢步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/拽步" title="zhuai4 bu4">拽步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/散步" title="san4 bu4">散步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/敛步" title="lian3 bu4">敛步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/横步" title="heng2 bu4">横步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/款步" title="kuan3 bu4">款步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/止步" title="zhi3 bu4">止步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/正步" title="zheng4 bu4">正步</a>, <a href="/dictionary/步伐" title="bu4 fa2">步伐</a>, <a href="/dictionary/步入" title="bu4 ru4">步入</a>, <a href="/dictionary/步兵" title="bu4 bing1">步兵</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">步[<span style="color:#000099;">Bù</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- surname Bu<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">步[<span style="color:#0